'''''The New World Order''''' is a book written by [[H. G. Wells]], originally published in January 1940. Wells expressed the idea that a '[[New world order (politics)|new world order]]' should be formed to unite the nations of the world in order to bring peace and end war.
''The New World Order'' also advocates a legal system that would protect 
the [[human rights|Rights of Man]]. <ref>Partington, John S. ''Building Cosmopolis: The Political Thought of H.G. Wells''. 
Ashgate Publishing, Ltd., 2003. {{ISBN|0754633837}}   (p. 127).</ref>
It was republished in 2007 under {{ISBN|1-59986-727-3}}.

